1
00:00:09,180 --> 00:00:09,980
Yang.

2
00:00:10,660 --> 00:00:11,620
It's been five hundred years.

3
00:00:12,220 --> 00:00:14,420
Every day I've channeled energy
to suppress Xieyun within you,

4
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:16,580
but there's been no improvement.

5
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:18,540
But I won't give up on you.

6
00:00:19,180 --> 00:00:21,140
I will find a way to heal you.

7
00:00:48,420 --> 00:00:49,260
Heng.

8
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:52,660
For five hundred years,

9
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:54,860
you've used your cultivation every day

10
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:56,500
trying to purge his fiendish aura.

11
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:59,100
If this goes on,

12
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,100
your body will break down.

13
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,220
For five hundred years,

14
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:04,260
you

15
00:01:04,460 --> 00:01:05,860
have also been using your cultivation

16
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:06,780
to channel energy to me.

17
00:01:07,620 --> 00:01:09,340
I'll be fine.

18
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:11,220
There's really nothing
I can do with you.

19
00:01:12,220 --> 00:01:13,060
But you need to understand,

20
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:15,540
even if you keep channeling
immortal energy into him,

21
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,740
it won't purify Xieyun inside him.

22
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:19,140
No matter what,

23
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:22,060
as long as he's my disciple,

24
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:24,140
I'll stand by him

25
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:26,180
and protect him.

26
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:31,080
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 12]

27
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:35,260
The Nine Heavens Nectar

28
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,260
can repair a damaged immortal soul.

29
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:38,940
Take it.

30
00:01:43,980 --> 00:01:44,980
Thank you, Immortal Venerable.

31
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:48,860
He was already dying.

32
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,940
Why make such a sacrifice

33
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,340
for him?

34
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,500
It was my failure to guard
the Fushi Mirror

35
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:57,140
that allowed Xieyun to escape.

36
00:01:57,780 --> 00:01:59,940
Yaoyang is innocent.

37
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:01,660
He shouldn't have to pay for it.

38
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:03,580
Did you risk entering
the forbidden grounds

39
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,100
for him as well?

40
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:08,820
I heard Xieyun

41
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:10,700
was born from the forbidden grounds.

42
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:11,740
I've already found...

43
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,820
Don't waste your effort.

44
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:15,900
Xieyun can't be destroyed.

45
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,460
It can only be sealed away.

46
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:19,740
You can't save him.

47
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:26,780
Immortal Venerable,

48
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,460
I've collected the four sacred plants

49
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,780
and nourished them with the water

50
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,460
of Wanxian Spring as you instructed.

51
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,540
Once they fully grow,
we can extract their essence

52
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,740
to repair the Fushi Mirror.

53
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,380
Repair the Fushi Mirror?

54
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:39,780
Exactly.

55
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:41,700
Only the Fushi Mirror

56
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:44,180
can truly seal away Xieyun.

57
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,740
What rotten luck.

58
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:57,500
The training grounds

59
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:59,620
are for disciples of the immortal sect.

60
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:00,940
You, a vessel of evil,

61
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:02,060
get out of here.

62
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,700
Don't mess up this place!

63
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:04,820
Exactly.

64
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:05,860
You little fiend,

65
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:07,420
get lost!

66
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:12,780
Who knows if Immortal Master Xiyin
is blind

67
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:14,380
or just foolish

68
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:17,100
to take in a fiend like this
as a disciple.

69
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,700
You can insult me,

70
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:20,740
but not my master!

71
00:03:34,340 --> 00:03:35,940
The Shadow Clan has come after us
time and again,

72
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,060
all because of you!

73
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:38,380
Today, we'll kill this jinx

74
00:03:38,540 --> 00:03:40,260
and cleanse our ranks!

75
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:44,580
Stop!

76
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,300
Immortal Xiyin,

77
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:59,380
he started it!

78
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:00,540
Exactly.

79
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:02,180
You can't show favoritism just because

80
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,260
he's your disciple.

81
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,100
Let's go!

82
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:25,900
Yang.

83
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,140
Just now,

84
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:28,620
you were attacked
by the fiendish aura again.

85
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,340
They disrespected you!

86
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:32,300
Yang,

87
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:33,940
I'm glad

88
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:35,620
you want to protect me.

89
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:36,620
But

90
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:39,020
I care more about you.

91
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:41,780
From now on, no matter what happens,

92
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:43,460
you must learn to control your emotions.

93
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:45,780
You must not let the fiendish aura

94
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,580
take control and lose your mind.

95
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:49,340
In this world,

96
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:52,620
only you truly care for me.

97
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:55,100
What foolish talk is that?

98
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:56,860
You are my disciple.

99
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,340
Of course I'll protect you.

100
00:05:05,700 --> 00:05:06,860
Master.

101
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:10,140
I promise I will save you.

102
00:05:24,420 --> 00:05:25,220
Master.

103
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,820
So when you stabbed me,

104
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,740
you were stopping me
from turning into a fiend.

105
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:32,780
You sacrificed yourself

106
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,900
just to give me a peaceful life.

107
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:36,620
Don't worry.

108
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:37,940
From now on,

109
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,340
I'll stay by your side.

110
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:42,020
We'll

111
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:44,020
never be apart again.

112
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:26,220
♪Hundreds of days in the mortal world♪

113
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:30,140
♪Are but a single thought in heaven♪

114
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:33,540
♪Why does a single glance♪

115
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:37,220
♪Already steal my sleep?♪

116
00:06:37,780 --> 00:06:40,980
♪If the prophecy begins♪

117
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:44,540
♪No one shall escape its reach♪

118
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:50,820
♪In that very thought,
a boundary was drawn♪

119
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:55,230
♪This life feels like our first sight♪

120
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:59,110
♪For you, I drew the Three-Lives Blade♪

121
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:05,940
♪Carving eternity before your eyes♪

122
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:09,620
♪If saying goodbye aloud♪

123
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:13,500
♪Allows us to meet again♪

124
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:14,980
You're finally awake.

125
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:19,300
♪Please remember your promise♪

126
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,020
I...

127
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,660
After her revival,
she won't remember anything from before.

128
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,100
She's like a blank slate.

129
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:28,380
She understands nothing.

130
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:33,020
A blank slate.

131
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:48,820
This

132
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:50,580
is how you wear the flower.

133
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,940
She's the embodiment of Master.

134
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,020
Might as well

135
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:02,660
let her take Master's surname, Bai.

136
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,220
What should I call her?

137
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,460
You'll be called

138
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:15,020
Bai Ruoxi.

139
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:17,780
Bai...

140
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:18,980
Bai.

141
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:19,900
Ruo.

142
00:08:20,660 --> 00:08:21,420
Xi.

143
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:51,240
♪What is flickering?♪

144
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:53,980
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

145
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:59,980
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

146
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:02,860
♪What is falling?♪

147
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:06,100
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

148
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:11,540
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

149
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:14,060
♪When petals drift down♪

150
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:15,560
♪When the rain falls all around♪

151
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:18,260
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

152
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:20,120
♪Beyond the dunes♪

153
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:21,500
♪No end in sight♪

154
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:24,500
♪I am like a mayfly♪

155
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:26,060
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

156
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:27,560
♪Nor will I run away♪

157
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:30,520
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

158
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:35,780
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

159
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:52,840
♪What is flickering?♪

160
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:55,540
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

161
00:09:55,740 --> 00:10:01,540
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

162
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:04,780
♪What is falling?♪

163
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:07,720
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

164
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:12,940
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

165
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:15,540
♪When petals drift down♪

166
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:17,040
♪When the rain falls all around♪

167
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:19,700
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
